# --- Action Pre/Post Conditions (noria:ActionPreCondition, noria:ActionPostCondition) ---
<https://w3id.org/noria/data/actionprecondition/RouterBackupComplete> a noria:ActionPreCondition ;
    rdfs:label "Router Configuration Backup Complete"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Ensures that a full backup of the router configuration has been successfully performed before proceeding."@en .

<https://w3id.org/noria/data/actionpostcondition/RouterFunctionalityVerified> a noria:ActionPostCondition ;
    rdfs:label "Router Functionality Verified"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Confirms that the router is fully operational, routing traffic correctly, and all interfaces are up after the upgrade."@en .

<https://w3id.org/noria/data/actionprecondition/DatabaseBackupComplete> a noria:ActionPreCondition ;
    rdfs:label "Database Backup Complete"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Verifies that a recent and valid backup of the database exists."@en .

<https://w3id.org/noria/data/actionpostcondition/DatabaseAccessVerified> a noria:ActionPostCondition ;
    rdfs:label "Database Access Verified"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Confirms that applications can successfully connect to and query the migrated database."@en .

